Leopod is a podcast subscription manager and player designed for elementary OS.
Subscribe to RSS feeds of podcasts, download episodes, and listen to them.
It provides following features:
- Subscribing to RSS Feeds
- Downloading Audio Files
- Playing Audio Files
- Checking Feeds for updated information periodically
- Remembering the last played position of each episode

WWW: https://github.com/leggettc18/leopod
